org.wso2.carbon.repository
Class Activity

java.lang.Object
  org.wso2.carbon.repository.Activity

public class Activity
extends Object

Representation of a activity that has been performed on the repository. For example, a put operation will lead to activity of adding a resource into the repository, or updating an existing resource on the repository. Each activity performed on the repository will have a corresponding log entry, which is a record of a single action performed on the repository.
